PC PC_BusRider@BusRider
atom :'board'
process BusRider@board
process OnBus@OpOnBus
after board->OnBus
operator OpOnBus.IntChoice
atom :'seat'
atom :'stand'
atom :'move'
atom :'alight'
op_connector OpOnBus->seat
op_connector OpOnBus->stand
op_connector OpOnBus->move
op_connector OpOnBus->alight
reference RefOnBus
after seat->RefOnBus
after stand->RefOnBus
after move->RefOnBus
ref_connector RefOnBus->OnBus
